snippet.title: Meet Juliette | Omega Strikers Character Trailer
snippet.description:
To reach the pinnacle of the Pro League—that’s Juliette’s dream. 

💻 Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1869590/Omega_Strikers/
🍎 Pre-order on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/omega-strikers/id1582532342
🤖 Pre-reg on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.odysseyinteractive.omegastrikers
🎮 Pre-order on Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/omega-strikers-switch/

Listen to the Japanese, English, and karaoke versions of Juliette's theme: GO STRIKE!

On YouTube: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=OLAK5uy_kOAUmp8ddqeSEBuSoLA9ZspYMuL2tjJxc
On Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/1nk4TSNFpml9KMG2pWY51d?si=mSWfpf0XSiiNsxvERPm3kw
